                {
                  "id": "description",
                  "contents": [
                    {
                      "list": [
                        "The information supplied is collected by the Office for National Statistics (ONS), on behalf of the Office of Rail and Road (ORR), under Ministerial Direction.",
                        "You cannot appeal your selection. Your business was selected to give us a comprehensive view of the UK economy.",
                        "We will treat your data securely and confidentially.",
                        "Data should relate to sites in England, Scotland and Wales.",
                        "You can provide informed estimates if actual figures are not available.",
                        "Please provide your figures rounded to the nearest whole number.",
                        "You can save a copy of your answers at the end of this questionnaire using the &#x2018;Download as PDF&#x2019; button."
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "preview_content": {
                "id": "preview",
                "title": "Information you need",
                "contents": [
                  {
                    "description": "This survey asks for the <strong>value of acquisitions and proceeds from disposals </strong>for each of the following:"
                  }
                ],
                "questions": [
                  {
                    "question": "Track and signalling",
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "description": "<strong>Include:</strong>"
                      },
                      {
                        "list": [
                          "expenditure on rail track renewals and enhancements",
                          "new routes",
                          "new electrification and signalling and any associated land",
                          "professional fees and charges"
                        ]
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "question": "Rolling stock",
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "description": "<strong>Include:</strong>"
                      },
                      {
                        "list": [
                          "new and second-hand acquisitions of rail rolling stock",
                          "eligible refurbishment work"
                        ]
                      },
                      {
                        "description": "<strong>Exclude:</strong>"
                      },
                      {
                        "list": ["leasing charges"]
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "question": "Stations",
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "description": "<strong>Include:</strong>"
                      },
                      {
                        "list": [
                          "expenditure on passenger stations",
                          "passenger and freight train depots, train maintenance facilities",
                          "expenditure on retail outlets"
                        ]
                      },
                      {
                        "description": "<strong>Exclude:</strong>"
                      },
                      {
                        "list": ["expenditure at station ticket offices"]
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "question": "Other rail",
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "description": "<strong>Include:</strong>"
                      },
                      {
                        "list": [
                          "all other expenditure in connection with rail business",
                          "buildings and associated land",
                          "non-rail vehicles",
                          "capital equipment"
                        ]
                      },
                      {
                        "description": "<strong>Exclude:</strong>"
                      },
                      {
                        "list": [
                          "track and signalling",
                          "expenditure not connected with rail business"
                        ]
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              "secondary_content": [
                {
                  "id": "secondary-content",
                  "contents": [
                    {
                      "title": "How we use your data"
                    },
                    {
                      "list": [
                        "The information you provide contributes to the rail finance statistical release by the Office for Rail and Road (ORR).",
                        "ORR aggregates the investment figures for all the companies in Great Britain and publishes them as a yearly estimate in the <a href=\"https://dataportal.orr.gov.uk/statistics/finance/rail-industry-finance/table-7290-private-sector-investment-in-the-rail-industry-excludes-network-rail-investment/\"target=\"_blank\"rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">rail finance statistical release (this link opens in a new tab)</a>."
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
